texts.orig: I was driven to share my knowledge from the start of my professional career. With the internet came blogs, and I bought some domain names. I started writing about my personal life on coenradie.com (no longer available), and for my professional career, we started a website called https://gridshore.nl (no longer available). I wrote a lot of blogs, but employers started to have blogs as well. Therefore, I moved most of my writing to corporate blogs.

I started writing about my personal life on coenradie.com (no longer available), and for my professional career, we started a website called https://gridshore.nl (no longer available). I wrote a lot of blogs, but employers started to have blogs as well. Therefore, I moved most of my writing to corporate blogs.

texts.label: text
texts.orig: Time has passed, and I sometimes feel the urge to write about something that is not necessarily suitable for the company I work for. That is what this blog is about. If I write something on my company's blog, I'll tell it here as well.
